565
00:24:06,923 --> 00:24:08,098
Jess...

566
00:24:08,142 --> 00:24:10,884
this is Daniel Shapiro.

567
00:24:10,927 --> 00:24:12,494
A pleasure.

568
00:24:12,538 --> 00:24:15,454
