611
00:26:20,361 --> 00:26:22,885
Good God, no.

612
00:26:22,929 --> 00:26:25,801
I'm rejecting his recommendation
for termination.

613
00:26:25,845 --> 00:26:29,022
I'm announcing that at a press
conference tomorrow morning.

614
00:26:29,065 --> 00:26:31,328
That's it?

615
00:26:33,287 --> 00:26:35,506
Passing the buck,
that's all that is.

616
00:26:35,550 --> 00:26:37,160
All due respect.

617
