None taken.

618
00:26:40,686 --> 00:26:43,340
You got to shut this down,
once and for all.

619
00:26:43,384 --> 00:26:45,647
Shout it out loud to city hall,

620
00:26:45,691 --> 00:26:47,518
to the A.G. up in Albany,

621
00:26:47,562 --> 00:26:50,826
to the civil courts judges:
no more going after this guy.

