00:27:04,057 --> 00:27:07,538
And yesterday, my wife
had a bottle thrown at her.

627
00:27:07,582 --> 00:27:10,063
Look, you want police escorts,
you got them.

628
00:27:10,106 --> 00:27:12,848
Who wants to live like that?

629
00:27:12,892 --> 00:27:15,851
And my children seeing me on TV,

630
00:27:15,895 --> 00:27:19,246
every step I take
like a perp walk?

631
00:27:22,118 --> 00:27:25,687
They used to look at me
like I was their hero.

632
00:27:32,259 --> 00:27:34,130
I didn't dismiss you, Detective.

633
00:27:36,176 --> 00:27:38,091
I'm sorry, Commissioner,

634
00:27:38,134 --> 00:27:42,312
but I won't put my family
through this any longer.

635
00:27:42,356 --> 00:27:44,358
Let's give the public
what it wants.

636
00:27:46,012 --> 00:27:47,578
And what's that?

637
00:27:47,622 --> 00:27:51,191
Me, gone.

638
00:27:59,155 --> 00:28:03,116
You walk away,
you're letting them win.

639
00:28:04,160 --> 00:28:06,162
They already have.

640
00:28:18,087 --> 00:28:19,175
Sir?

641
