moment with Ruby.

701
00:31:07,082 --> 00:31:08,388
It's okay.

702
00:31:45,729 --> 00:31:47,862
No!

703
00:31:48,907 --> 00:31:50,299
No...!

704
00:31:50,343 --> 00:31:52,519
Anthony. Anthony,
can you hear me?

705
00:31:54,651 --> 00:31:57,263
I think I found her.

706
00:31:57,306 --> 00:31:58,960
Hello?

707
00:32:00,440 --> 00:32:01,484
Anthony, hello?

708
00:32:02,529 --> 00:32:04,270
Who are you talking to, Jess?

709
00:32:04,313 --> 00:32:05,401
Police!

710
00:32:05,445 --> 00:32:06,750
Hands off me!

711
00:32:11,320 --> 00:32:13,496
Don't fight me! Police!

712
00:32:16,195 --> 00:32:17,283
Hands where I can see them.

