00:35:19,595 --> 00:35:21,249
Yeah.

775
00:35:21,293 --> 00:35:23,947
Look, if you want,
we can give you an escort home.

776
00:35:23,991 --> 00:35:26,298
Guys, get onstage.

777
00:35:27,299 --> 00:35:28,474
My whole life,

778
00:35:28,517 --> 00:35:30,432
people have paid
for my mistakes.

